      "review_summary": "The PR adds text_end, thinking_end, toolcall_start, and toolcall_end to the opencode-go stalled-stream liveness predicate and adds a regression test for boundary-event idle resets.\n\nPR surface: Source +4, Tests +34. Total +38 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible. Current main forwards boundary events but only re-arms idle liveness on delta events, and the canonical issue includes a focused failing timing sequence; I did not run tests in this read-only review.",
